    `},{slug:"payment-options-bail-bonds",title:"Payment Options for Bail Bonds: Making Bail Affordable",excerpt:"Learn about flexible payment plans and options available for bail bonds in Delaware.",category:"Payment Options",readTime:"6 min read",date:"2026-03-09",image:"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-6726b3ff858f?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",content:`
